WEBVTT

00:02.001 --> 00:04.800
Please, not you!

00:04.800 --> 00:07.300
- You have to cross over. - I don't want to.

00:08.000 --> 00:10.600
I saw Jim's ghost step into Sam's body.

00:11.600 --> 00:12.740
You're back!

00:12.800 --> 00:14.070
Do I know you?

00:14.140 --> 00:16.000
Look,I see the same guy that you see...

00:16.070 --> 00:17.440
Different hair, nose,eyes,

00:17.500 --> 00:19.040
It's not Jim.

00:19.100 --> 00:21.300
He's in there somewhere. He just has to be.

00:21.370 --> 00:22.540
You're not going to tell me

00:22.600 --> 00:23.540
You think I'm your husband reincarnated.

00:23.600 --> 00:24.800
Because you're the only sane person

00:24.870 --> 00:26.540
I've met since I woke up.

00:26.600 --> 00:27.870
It's not much, but maybe

00:27.870 --> 00:29.140
you could help me finish my garage,

00:29.200 --> 00:30.800
And you could live there while you do the work,

00:30.870 --> 00:32.369
Just until you figure out your next move.

00:32.439 --> 00:34.640
Oh,my god,it's true. You don't know who I am,do you?

00:34.700 --> 00:35.870
You must be Nicole.

00:35.940 --> 00:37.120
The fiance?

00:37.120 --> 00:39.440
She is not his fiance until he puts a ring on her finger.

00:39.500 --> 00:40.800
Bye.

00:43.200 --> 00:44.470
Bye.

